cal potential and bias voltage. At last we study how\nenergy level degeneracy can increase the output power.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Feb 2017 16:08:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 28 Jun 2017 08:54:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-06-29"}
