\nphysical interpretation of the observed behaviour in the frame of a simple\none-dimensional model of the polar emitting region with a collisionless shock\nformed in the infalling plasma near the neutron star surface. With this model,\nwe are able to reproduce the observed variations of the continuum hardness\nratio and of the CRSF energy with luminosity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Feb 2017 12:55:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-22"}
